description:
&lt;p&gt;This is a hugely exciting time to be a part of Mid and South Essex NHS Foundation Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We merged three acute Trusts in April 2020 and, as a senior member of the communication and engagement team, you will have a key role to play. Leading the internal communications across the new organisation, you will help to shape the future of one of the largest hospital Trusts in the NHS.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We want to harness the opportuntities of being a new, merged organisation, using excellent communication and engagement to support, energise and empower our workforce.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a dynamic, experienced comms professional who can build excellent relationships and bring boundless enthusiasm to our friendly and growing team. If that sounds like you, we&#39;d love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameNiki EvesJob titleAssociate Director, Communications and EngagementEmail addressniki.eves@meht.nhs.ukTelephone number01245 516641&lt;/p&gt;
